name: Arcanum
description: Carpe Noctem. Meaning “mystery” or “secret,” Arcanum blends cinnamon spice, delicious coconut, sensual osmanthus with a medley of incense anchoring the enigmatic and cryptic aura of the fragrance until dark amberwoods, intoxicating vanilla, and beguiling tonka bean conclude the olfactory aria.
